</b></p>
<p><b>spectrum of different policy areas and human rights situations 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Norway); 
</b></p>
<p> 98.25. <b>Work with all sectors including the education sector, to ensure the 
</b>National Human Rights Institute effectively supports the country&#8217;s 
</p>
<p><b>commitment to human rights (Australia); 
</b></p>
<p> 98.26. <b>Continue to assist, when requested, Aruba, Cura&#231;ao and Sint 
Maarten to develop human rights institutions, laws and policies 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Australia); 
</b></p>
<p> 98.27. <b>Formulate a national human rights action plan (Philippines); 
</b></p>
<p> 98.28. <b>Develop a national human rights action plan (Uzbekistan); 
</b></p>
<p> 98.29. <b>Evaluate the possibility to develop a national human rights action 
