</b></p>
<p><b>particular Muslim migrants (Egypt); 
</b></p>
<p> 98.44. <b>Take further measures to combat discrimination in the labour 
market and combat in particular discrimination based on ethnic 
</b></p>
<p><b>origin and discrimination targeting transgender people (France); 
</b></p>
<p> 98.45. <b>Intensify efforts to combat the dissemination of ideas based on the 
